	WIELD <object> [#]
	READY <object> [#]
	  USE <object> [#]

Wield allows you to wield a weapon of some sort, as long as you 
are not already wielding one.  If you have proficiency in the 
type of weapon you are wielding, you will hit an opponent more 
frequently.  Your proficiency with a particular type of weapon 
will increase as you use it.

: inventory
You have a small bow, a long bow, a small ash bow.
: wield bow 3
You wield a small ash bow.

